    "knowledgeAssets":  [
                            {
                                "assetId":  "tcel-filing-disclosure-control-catalog-2026",
                                "docKey":  "tcel-filing-disclosure-control-catalog",
                                "title":  "TCEL T9-018-Filing-Disclosure-Knowledge Control Catalog",
                                "assetType":  "ReferenceManual",
                                "docType":  "ControlCatalog",
                                "issuer":  "TCEL",
                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: FK-030 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "FK-001 Approved applicability required | Preventive | Block filing without T9-006 applicability approval | Critical | CCO/General Counsel. FK-002 Regulatory calendar owner required | Preventive | Reject calendar item without owner | High | Filing Owner. FK-003 Due-date and escalation control | Corrective | Escalate by severity as due date approaches | Critical | Filing Owner. FK-004 Source data completeness | Preventive | Block filing if source data incomplete | Critical | Filing Owner. FK-005 Source reconciliation | Preventive | Block filing if unreconciled | Critical | Accounting. FK-006 Filing validation | Preventive | Reject invalid form/schema | Critical | Filing Owner. FK-007 Authorized filing approver | Preventive | Reject unauthorized approval | Critical | CCO. FK-008 Authorized signatory | Preventive | Reject unauthorized signature | Critical | General Counsel. FK-009 Submission confirmation required | Evidence | Block closure without confirmation | Critical | Filing Owner. FK-010 Immutable filed version | Evidence | Block mutation of filed record | Critical | Filing Owner. FK-011 Amendment workflow | Preventive | Require documented amendment process | High | Filing Owner. FK-012 Late filing escalation | Corrective | Escalate to CCO/Board | Critical | CCO. FK-013 Disclosure source validation | Preventive | Block if source unverified | Critical | Disclosure Owner. FK-014 Disclosure legal/compliance review | Preventive | Require CCO/General Counsel sign-off | Critical | CCO/General Counsel. FK-015 Approved disclosure publication | Governance | Block publication until approved | Critical | Disclosure Owner. FK-016 Certified performance only | Preventive | Reject uncertified performance in disclosure | Critical | Head of Performance. FK-017 Distribution recipient control | Preventive | Restrict to approved recipient list | High | Disclosure Owner. FK-018 Secure distribution | Preventive | Require encrypted/controlled channel | Critical | Security. FK-019 Attestation signer identity | Preventive | Verify signer identity before recording | Critical | Compliance. FK-020 No AI signature or certification | Preventive | Deny AI signing/certification action | Critical | AI Governance. FK-021 Knowledge source and approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved knowledge into active set | Critical | Data Governance. FK-022 Stale knowledge restriction | Preventive | Mark stale and exclude from active retrieval | High | Data Governance. FK-023 Privileged knowledge access | Preventive | Need-to-know enforcement | Critical | Legal/CCO. FK-024 Mandatory training assignment | Preventive | Assign per role requirement | High | HR/Compliance. FK-025 Training completion evidence | Evidence | Require completion record | High | HR/Compliance. FK-026 Competency threshold | Preventive | Restrict role activity below threshold | High | HR/Compliance. FK-027 No AI training waiver | Preventive | Deny AI waiver of mandatory training | Critical | AI Governance. FK-028 Legal hold overrides deletion | Preventive | Block deletion under hold | Critical | Legal. FK-029 Retention enforcement | Preventive | Auto-purge per retention schedule | High | Data Governance. FK-030 Cross-tenant access denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. FK-031 No AI filing submission | Preventive | Deny AI submission permission | Critical | AI Governance. FK-032 No AI disclosure publication | Preventive | Deny AI publication permission | Critical | AI Governance. FK-033 Superseded version retention | Evidence | Preserve prior version | High | Data Governance. FK-034 External report approval | Preventive | Require approval before external release | Critical | CCO. FK-035 Downstream correction notification | Corrective | Notify affected recipients/systems | High | Filing Owner."
                            }
                        ]
